<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MedIQ Link - ระบบสรุปรายได้ทันตแพทย์ 6 สาขา</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.sheetjs.com/xlsx-latest/package/dist/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+Thai:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary: #0f766e;
            --primary-light: #14b8a6;
            --primary-rgb: 15, 118, 110;
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
            --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #4f46e5 100%);
            
            --success: #059669;
            --success-bg: #ecfdf5;
            --danger: #dc2626;
            --danger-bg: #fef2f2;
            
            --neutral-50: #f8fafc;
            --neutral-100: #f1f5f9;
            --neutral-200: #e2e8f0;
            --neutral-300: #cbd5e1;
            --neutral-400: #94a3b8;
            --neutral-600: #475569;
            --neutral-700: #334155;
            --neutral-800: #1e293b;
            --neutral-900: #0f172a;
            
            --radius-sm: 8px;
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --radius-lg: 18px;
            --radius-xl: 24px;
            
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
            --shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
            
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            --glass-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, #f0f4f8 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--neutral-800);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .wrap {
            max-width: 1440px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        /* Hero / Header Section */
        .hero {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-content {
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .hero h1 svg {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            fill: currentColor;
            animation: pulse-slow 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Glassmorphic Panel Base */
        .panel {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 28px;
            box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
        }

        /* Upload Container & Dropzone */
        .upload-box {
            border: 2px dashed #93c5fd;
            background: rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.5);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 36px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .upload-box:hover, .upload-box.dragover {
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
            background: rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.15);
        }

        .upload-box strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--neutral-900);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .upload-box svg.cloud-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            margin: 0 auto 16px;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }

        /* File Chips */
        .file-chips-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .file-chip {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .file-chip svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .file-chip .file-size {
            color: var(--neutral-400);
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        input[type="file"] {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Buttons & Actions */
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        button {
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px 0 rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.25);
            transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        button:hover:not(:disabled) {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.35);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        button:active:not(:disabled) {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        button.secondary {
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--neutral-700);
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        button.secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
            background: var(--neutral-50);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            color: var(--neutral-900);
        }

        button.warn {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px 0 rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
        }

        button:disabled {
            opacity: 0.45;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            transform: none !important;
        }

        .status {
            margin-top: 16px;
            color: var(--neutral-600);
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 90%;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        /* KPI Summary Grid */
        .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(210px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 22px;
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
            border-color: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.3);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--neutral-400);
        }

        .card.c-branches::before { background: #3b82f6; }
        .card.c-doctors::before { background: #6366f1; }
        .card.c-income::before { background: #10b981; }
        .card.c-df::before { background: #f59e0b; }
        .card.c-clinic::before { background: #06b6d4; }
        .card.c-gross::before { background: #8b5cf6; }
        .card.c-net::before { background: #e11d48; }

        .card .card-header-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .card .label {
            color: var(--neutral-600);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .card .card-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            color: var(--neutral-400);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .card.c-branches .card-icon { color: #3b82f6; }
        .card.c-doctors .card-icon { color: #6366f1; }
        .card.c-income .card-icon { color: #10b981; }
        .card.c-df .card-icon { color: #f59e0b; }
        .card.c-clinic .card-icon { color: #06b6d4; }
        .card.c-gross .card-icon { color: #8b5cf6; }
        .card.c-net .card-icon { color: #e11d48; }

        .card .value {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--neutral-900);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        /* Tabs Navigation */
        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            background: var(--neutral-100);
            padding: 6px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        .tab {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--neutral-600);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            transform: none !important;
        }

        .tab:hover {
            color: var(--neutral-900);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }

        .tab.active {
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm) !important;
        }

        /* Toolbar / Filters */
        .toolbar {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .toolbar input,
        .toolbar select {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            min-width: 240px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: #fff;
            outline: none;
        }

        .toolbar input:focus,
        .toolbar select:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.15);
        }

        .toolbar button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* Table & Custom Inputs */
        .table-wrap {
            overflow: auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 14px;
            min-width: 1000px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--neutral-100);
            text-align: right;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        th {
            background: var(--neutral-50);
            color: var(--neutral-700);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 13px;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 5;
        }

        td:first-child,
        th:first-child {
            text-align: left;
            position: sticky;
            left: 0;
            background: inherit;
            z-index: 10;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--neutral-100);
        }

        th:first-child {
            z-index: 15;
            background: var(--neutral-50);
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background: var(--neutral-50);
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: 0;
            background: var(--neutral-50) !important;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .money {
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        tr:last-child .money {
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* Elegant inline table input */
        .input-cell-wrapper {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            width: 110px;
            min-width: 110px;
        }

        .input-cell-wrapper:focus-within {
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.15);
        }

        .input-cell {
            width: 100%;
            border: 0;
            background: transparent;
            padding: 4px;
            text-align: right;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13.5px;
            color: var(--neutral-800);
            outline: none;
            -moz-appearance: textfield;
        }

        /* Hide spin buttons for Chrome, Safari, Edge, Opera */
        .input-cell::-webkit-outer-spin-button,
        .input-cell::-webkit-inner-spin-button {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Badges */
        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .badge.ok {
            background: var(--success-bg);
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .badge.bad {
            background: var(--danger-bg);
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .muted {
            color: var(--neutral-600);
            font-size: 13.5px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Help Modal (วิธีเตรียมไฟล์) */
        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
            animation: fade-in 0.25s ease-out;
        }

        .modal-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            max-width: 850px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            animation: slide-up 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
        }

        .modal-header {
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: var(--neutral-50);
        }

        .modal-header h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--neutral-900);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .modal-close {
            background: transparent;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--neutral-400);
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 4px;
            line-height: 1;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            transform: none !important;
        }

        .modal-close:hover {
            color: var(--neutral-900);
        }

        .modal-body {
            padding: 24px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            max-height: 70vh;
        }

        /* Mock Excel table in Modal */
        .mock-excel-table-wrap {
            overflow: auto;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .mock-excel-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 12px;
            min-width: 700px;
        }

        .mock-excel-table th, .mock-excel-table td {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .mock-excel-table th {
            background: var(--neutral-100);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--neutral-600);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .mock-excel-table tr.header-row td {
            background: #fdf2f8;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #be185d;
        }

        .mock-excel-table tr.subheader-row td {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #15803d;
        }

        .mock-excel-table tr.footer-row td {
            background: #eff6ff;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1d4ed8;
        }

        .mock-excel-table td.col-idx {
            font-weight: 600;
            background: var(--neutral-50);
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--neutral-400);
            width: 120px;
        }

        .tips-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .tip-item {
            background: var(--neutral-50);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .tip-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--neutral-900);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes pulse-slow {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 0.9; }
        }

        @keyframes fade-in {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slide-up {
            from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Responsive Breakpoints */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 28px;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 26px;
            }

            .cards {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .cards {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .wrap {
                padding: 16px;
            }
            
            .toolbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            
            .toolbar input, .toolbar select {
                min-width: 100%;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <!-- Header Branding -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M19 3H5C3.9 3 3 3.9 3 5V19C3 20.1 3.9 21 5 21H19C20.1 21 21 20.1 21 19V5C21 3.9 20.1 3 19 3M19 19H5V5H19V19M17 12H14V9H10V12H7V16H10V19H14V16H17V12Z" />
                    </svg>
                    MedIQ Link
                </h1>
                <p>ระบบรวบรวมรายได้และประมวลผลทันตแพทย์เชื่อมโยง 6 สาขา ระบบจะสแกนหาหมวด Dentist Fee, ยอดรายได้คุณหมอ (Prov Share) ข้ามสาขา และจัดสัดส่วนหักค่าแลปแพทย์ให้อัตโนมัติอย่างแม่นยำ</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Dropzone Box -->
        <section class="panel">
            <div class="upload-box" id="dropZone">
                <svg class="cloud-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M15 13l-3-3m0 0l-3 3m3-3v12"></path>
                </svg>
                <strong>ลากและวางไฟล์ Excel สรุปรายได้สาขาที่นี่ หรือคลิกเพื่อเลือกไฟล์</strong>
                <div class="muted">รองรับไฟล์ Excel (.xlsx, .xls) ได้หลายไฟล์พร้อมกัน เช่น สาขา1.xlsx, สาขา2.xlsx</div>
                <input id="fileInput" type="file" multiple accept=".xlsx,.xls" />
                
                <!-- Processed list -->
                <div class="file-chips-container" id="uploadedFilesList"></div>

                <div class="actions" style="justify-content:center">
                    <button onclick="processSelectedFiles()">
                        <svg style="width:18px;height:18px" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12S6.5 22 12 22 22 17.5 22 12 17.5 2 12 2M12 20C7.6 20 4 16.4 4 12S7.6 4 12 4 20 7.6 20 12 16.4 20 12 20M12.5 7H11V13L16.2 16.2L17 15L12.5 12.2V7Z"/></svg>
                        เริ่มประมวลผล Excel
                    </button>
                    <button class="secondary" onclick="clearAll()">
